ca.ualberta.cs.c301f12t01.testing
Class TextResponseTest

java.lang.Object
  ca.ualberta.cs.c301f12t01.testing.TextResponseTest

public class TextResponseTest
extends java.lang.Object

TextResponseTest -- Tests the TextResponse class to make sure all its methods work. This class test to see if a TextResponse is created properly by first testing to see if it exists. Then tests the getText method that gets the text of the TextResponse. After it will test to see if setResponseData converts Serializable into String and then see if it matches the pre-existing string. The last one tests to see if the getResponseData returns the serializable and that if it is converted to a String it matches the pre-existing string.
